<plot>Gong-yup and Un-young have been married for ten years. After a petty argument one night, Un-young throws her husband out on the streets. Gong-yup goes on a date with his mistress Hee-bong. When Un-young finds out about this, she demands a divorce from him. The two separate but Gong-yup tries to win Un-young back by proposing a family ski trip. The couple begin to feel romance rekindled on this trip but once again Gong-yup ruins things by refusing to end it with Hee-bong.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?179735</url></doc>
